endrendrum kadhal ( tamil : என்றென்றும் காதல் ; english : forever love ) is a tamil romantic drama film which released in 1999 written , directed and co-produced by manoj bhatnagar . the film stars vijay and rambha in the lead roles with raghuvaran and bhanupriya in other pivotal roles . veteran actor m. n. nambiar also played a supporting role , while manoj bhatnagar also composed the film 's music . the film opened to mixed reviews and was an average at the box office .